<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1437,152,720]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,332,476,503]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Discussion.</emphasis>
By its gonostylus, 
<taxonomicName authority="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík, 2019" authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" box="[554,823,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tkoci" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[554,823,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Pseudoaerumnosa tkoci</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[832,897,477,503]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[832,897,477,503]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
resembles 
<taxonomicName authority="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík, 2019" authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" box="[1026,1123,478,503]" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annae" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[1026,1123,478,503]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">P. annae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1132,1197,477,503]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1132,1197,477,503]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
and the sympatric 
<taxonomicName authority="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík, 2019" authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="formosa" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">P. formosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[251,315,513,539]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[251,315,513,539]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
but differs from both in having a medially constricted eye bridge, a more setose face, a longer R5, extending beyond the level of the base of the M-fork, in having a longer gonostylus with a less setose medial lobe and a longer tegmen with only narrow lateral sclerotizations. For differences between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" box="[1116,1212,586,611]" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annae">
<emphasis box="[1116,1212,586,611]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">P. annae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" box="[1267,1387,585,611]" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="formosa">
<emphasis box="[1267,1387,585,611]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">P. formosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, see under 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Vilkamaa &amp; Halenius &amp; Ševčík" authorityYear="2019" box="[222,317,622,647]" class="Insecta" family="Sciaridae" genus="Pseudoaerumnosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annae">
<emphasis box="[222,317,622,647]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">P. annae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
