<collectingRegion box="[1222,1300,657,683]" country="Czech Republic" name="Praha" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Prague</collectingRegion>
(Czech Re- public), who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[449,551,693,719]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
